Search Arizona homes for sale with the Arizona Key Team. We are a full service Arizona real estate team in the Phoenix metropolitan. We provide the area's most powerful real-time search and knowledge base allowing for our customers to stay ahead of the market.

--Free Account Registration--
By registering for a free search account you gain the ability to:

✔ Save your searches. 
✔ Receive daily property search updates.
✔ Take notes and mark your favorite properties.
✔ Easily communicate with your agent.
✔ Login with Facebook, Google, or Yahoo.
✔ Easily recall your recently visited properties
✔ Print your favorite properties.
✔ View nearby schools & school districts.
✔ Get Walk Scores for each property.
✔ Instantly view similar active listings.
✔ Schedule showings or ask questions.
✔ Google Street View on many listings.

Mobile Users
Go ahead and grab your smartphone and search Arizona properties on the go. Access your saved searches, favorite properties and notes right from your phone.

Real estate search areas covered by the Arizona Key Team include: Anthem, Ahwatukee, Apache Junction, Avondale, Buckeye, Carefree, Casa Grande, Cave Creek, Chandler, Coolidge, El Mirage, Eloy, Flagstaff, Florence, Fountain Hills, Gilbert, Glendale, Globe, Gold Canyon, Goodyear, Kingman, Lake Havasu, Litchfield Park, Maricopa, Mesa, Paradise Valley, Payson, Peoria, Prescott, Queen Creek, Rio Verde, Safford, San Tan Valley, Scottsdale, Sedona, Show Low, Sun City, Sun City West, Sun Lakes, Surprise, Tempe, Tolleson, Tonopah, Tucson, Waddell, Wickenburg & Yuma.

Search through our Arizona real estate knowledge base and stay on top of the current real estate market. Our knowledge base is a collection of information which is collected, organized, shared, and searched. It is intended to act as a resource for our customers provided through this website, as it offers answers to frequently asked questions, common real estate practices and helpful articles/blogs. Our knowledge base is designed and intended for growth, offering our existing and future customers a solution to their adventures in real estate ownership.
